Łuka  () is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Rozogi, within Szczytno County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  south-west of Rozogi,  south-east of Szczytno, and  south-east of the regional capital Olsztyn.
